data.description: Beautiful home in the Stonehedge subdivision, You will love the Open floor plan, Mocha color cabnets, island bar, breakfest bar, Large living area. Enjoy your own space in the Primary bedroom large enough for a sitting area. Primary bathroom has double sink vanity with seprate tub and shower. Carpet in the bedrooms, tile in the kitchen, Living, utility and bathrooms. Split floor plan with the utility room close to the garage and the the kids, right where you need it.
